      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Opossum.Exceptions.AppendConditionFailedException",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Opossum.Exceptions.AppendConditionFailedException.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Exception thrown when an append condition fails during event appending.\nThis is the single exception type that represents an optimistic concurrency conflict\nas defined by the DCB specification.</p>\n<p>\n<xref href=\"Opossum.Exceptions.ConcurrencyException\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is a subclass of this exception and is thrown by\nthe file-system layer for internal ledger-level races. Callers should always catch\n<xref href=\"Opossum.Exceptions.AppendConditionFailedException\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> — this covers both cases.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Opossum.Exceptions.ConcurrencyException.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Opossum.Exceptions.ConcurrencyException.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Opossum.Exceptions.ConcurrencyException",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Opossum.Exceptions.ConcurrencyException.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Exception thrown by the file-system event store for internal ledger-level concurrency\nconflicts (e.g. a stale <xref href=\"Opossum.Core.AppendCondition.AfterSequencePosition\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> check).</p>\n<p>\nThis is a subclass of <xref href=\"Opossum.Exceptions.AppendConditionFailedException\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>. Callers should\ncatch <xref href=\"Opossum.Exceptions.AppendConditionFailedException\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> rather than this type directly, \nunless they need to inspect the <xref href=\"Opossum.Exceptions.ConcurrencyException.ExpectedSequence\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> / <xref href=\"Opossum.Exceptions.ConcurrencyException.ActualSequence\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nproperties for diagnostic purposes.\n</p>\n"
    },
